description:
As a LPA Planning Officer
    I want to be redirected to already-submitted page
    So that Completed questionnaire cannot be submitted twice

elements.name: LPA Officer navigates to any page of submitted questionnaire

steps.name: an appeal has been created
a questionnaire has been created
the questionnaire has been completed
the LPA Planning Officer is authenticated
the LPA Questionnaire is submitted
the LPA Planning Officer is trying to access "task list" of already submitted questionnaire
the LPA Planning Officer is presented with already submitted page
the Already Submitted page should have Enquiries Email link
the Already Submitted page should have link to Call charges
